name: MRF89 AT Module
body:
### About MRF89 AT Module.
This module is based on the MRF89XA8 (868 MHz) or MRF89XA9 (915 MHz) RF module and MSP430FR5969 micro-controller from Texas Instruments.
Module can be controlled over UART with AT commands. As the module takes many signal lines for communication, this interface makes possible to reduce the number of signal lines significantly and make the communication interface very easy and understandable.

First version of the PCB is ready and is being manufactured for initial tests. After we have proved the designed module is working and you can make your own PCB or order it directly from the  [BreakMyBoard](www.breakmyboard.com) web page.
